[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說大方等修多羅王經",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948b24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後魏天竺三藏菩提流支譯",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞：一時婆伽婆，在王舍城迦蘭陀竹",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "園，與大比丘僧千二百五十人俱，及大菩薩摩訶薩眾。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948b29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，摩伽陀國頻婆娑羅王，出王舍城，詣迦蘭陀竹園精舍，至世尊所；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頭面禮足，遶佛三匝，退坐一面。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊即告頻婆娑羅王言：",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人夢中見於眾人，與諸婇女共相娛樂。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人覺已，憶念夢中眾人婇女。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是夢中眾人婇女，為有實不？",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」頻婆娑羅王答言：",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c06_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告大王：",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於意云何？",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人夢中見婇女，與諸人等共相娛樂。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "覺已憶念，如是之人寧有智不？",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」大王答言：",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無有眾人及眾婇女。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾人婇女尚不可得，何況當有共相娛樂？",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告大王：",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「凡夫之人亦復如是，眼見美色便生愛著，既生愛著便起欲心，既起欲心起瞋癡業，或作身業，或作口業，或作意業。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼所作業作已而滅，滅已不依東方而住，亦復不依南方而住，亦復不依西方而住，亦復不依北方而住，四維、上、下亦復如是。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至臨終時行識將滅，其意現前。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是行識，自作之業必盡受之。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人夢覺，不見婇女及諸人眾，行識滅已初識次生，或生天中，或生人中，或生地獄，或生畜生，或生餓鬼。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以初識不斷自心相續，應受報處而生其中。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀諸生滅頗有一法，從於今世至未來世。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是行識終時，名之為滅。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識起時，名之為生。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行識滅時，去無所至；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生時，無所從來。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識性離故。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c26_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行識行識空，滅時滅業空，初識初識空，生時生業空，觀諸業果亦不失壞。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王當知！",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以初識心相續不斷而受果報。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0948c29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時善逝說此語已，而說頌曰：",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一切唯名字，　　唯住想分別；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名字分別說，　　而說無所有。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以種種名字，　　說於種種法；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法中無如是，　　此法諸法相。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名字名字空，　　名字離名字；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸法無名字，　　以名字而說。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此法非實有，　　以分別而生；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼分別亦無，　　空以分別說。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切凡夫說，　　眼能見於色；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世間妄分別，　　取之以為實。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛之所說法，　　眾緣集故見；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此是行次第，　　為說第一義。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非眼見於色，　　意不覺諸法；",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此是第一諦，　　非世間所覺。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊說此經已，摩伽陀國頻婆娑羅王，一切世間天、人、阿修羅、揵闥婆等，聞佛所說，皆大歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說大方等修多羅王經",
        "from": "T14n0575_001:0949a19_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]